data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. This is your opportunity to own an affordable, move-in ready property in an OVERSIZED lot with no restrictions! Plenty of space for your all your big toys. Minutes away from the nearest public boat ramp with access to Little Manatee River, Terra Ceia Bay and the Gulf of Mexico. Home sits on a generous, CORNER fenced-in lot with an above-ground pool and sheds for storage. Great split floor plan offers a NICE AND BRIGHT living area on one side and VERY SPACIOUS bedrooms on the other. Ample kitchen with eating area, laundry room and a den/utility room! Most of the windows have been replaced with double pane, efficient ones. Newer laminate plank waterproof flooring throughout. Conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants, I-75 and everything that this booming area has to offer. NO HOA, NO CDD. MOVE-IN READY NOW!
